              <strong>Reishi</strong>
              <span>steady calm under load</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-empty" style="color:var(--earth-dk);font-weight:600;font-style:normal;">
            ✓ Dual-extracted · Fruiting body only · 2,000mg total
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COFFEE vs HAPPIE TIMELINE -->
  <section class="switch-section">
    <div class="switch-inner">
      <div class="switch-header">
        <div class="parallel-eyebrow">The 12-Hour Difference</div>
        <h2 class="parallel-title serif">What your morning <em>actually</em> looks like.</h2>
